FYI - Below are meeting notes from last week's Central Data Repository 
meeting.  

Summary.  
The challenge - there are many technical steps necessary to achieve a single 
data source for all of Enron.  Below are our team's immediate technical "To 
Do's".  
The good news - teams are continuing to work together to bring about a ONE 
Enron single source of data.  

Marie
